properties.Name: AtmService
properties.Description: The one ore more ATM Services that are offered at a specific ATM site/location.

Columns.Name: AtmId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ATM.

Columns.Name: AtmServiceTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ATM Service.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date that the ATM Service is offered at the Site.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date that the ATM Service is offered at the Site.

Columns.Name: AtmServiceFirstOfferedDate
Columns.Description: The first date that the ATM Service was offered at the ATM Site.

Columns.Name: AtmServicePlannedAbandonmentDate
Columns.Description: The planned abandonment date of the ATM Service at the ATM Site.

Columns.Name: LimitedAccessIndicator
Columns.Description: Limited access allows certain types of parties to make deposits and check balances at the ATM, but does not permit withdrawals.

Columns.Name: FullAccessIndicator
Columns.Description: Full ATM access offers the complete range of transactions including withdrawals and transfers between accounts.

Columns.Name: AtmServiceNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the ATM Service.
